                                MIAMI CHASE

Typed by PARASITE of LSD.


INTRODUCTION
        Armed with a Magnum and a Ferrari F40, you're no longer a regular
cop.  Take part in breathtaking street racing with extra turbos, injection
systems, wheelblades, oil cannons, spray glass, power steering, body kits
and more.  Bring the Hoodlums and creeps on the streets to Justice.

FEATURES
        Five huge Cities,
        Radar Surveilance,
        Incredible fast action,
        Radar surveillance.

CONTROLS
        As an undercover agent of the Drug Enforcement Agency (DEA), you
must seek out and apprehend all criminal gang members to proceed with the
next mission.
        To apprehend either shoot the criminal car or run it off the road.
The arch-criminal of each gang will be driving a Yellow Corvette.
        Once all criminals are brought to justice, find the EXIT shown by
four arrows, or an OUT sign to leave the map.
        You can buy add-ons for your car.  Use the radar to spot criminal
cars and 'head them off' by learning the streets.

CONTROLS DURING GAME
        Use the joystick to manouvre, and the <SPACE BAR> to display your
radar.

CONTROLS INSIDE GARAGE
        Use the joystick, press fire to select an icon, and then press UP to
purchase the add on, or DOWN to exit the garage.

        On the title menus, use joystick to move the highlight, and press
fire to select.

End.
